Subject: GtkImage: Add "use-fallback" property

So that icon-name and GIcon type of GtkImages can use automatic
fallback names.
---
Index: gtk+2.0-2.23.90/gtk/gtkimage.c
===================================================================
--- gtk+2.0-2.23.90.orig/gtk/gtkimage.c	2011-01-06 18:15:12.000000000 +0100
+++ gtk+2.0-2.23.90/gtk/gtkimage.c	2011-01-20 15:12:58.000000000 +0100
@@ -138,6 +138,7 @@
 
